{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"4000000000000001","type":"group","x":0,"y":1000,"width":1860,"height":900,"color":"3","label":"データフロー (人 ↔ ロボット, Azure Voice Live WS 経由)"},
		{"id":"1000000000000001","type":"group","x":0,"y":0,"width":1860,"height":360,"color":"3","label":"Composition (autoconnect)"},
		{"id":"2000000000000001","type":"group","x":0,"y":400,"width":920,"height":560,"color":"3","label":"unitree_go2_agentic_voice_live の追加スキル"},
		{"id":"3000000000000001","type":"group","x":940,"y":400,"width":920,"height":560,"color":"3","label":"unitree_go2_spatial の中身"},
		{"id":"0000000000000001","type":"text","text":"# unitree-go2-agentic-voice-live  構成図","x":20,"y":-90,"width":760,"height":50},
		{"id":"1000000000000002","type":"text","text":"**unitree_go2_agentic_voice_live**  (autoconnect)\n\nbrain = `AzureVoiceLiveAgent.blueprint(ptt_mode=True)` (gpt-realtime / ja-JP-NanamiNeural)  ·  system_prompt = `JAPANESE_SYSTEM_PROMPT`  ·  `.disabled_modules(SecurityModule)`","x":40,"y":40,"width":1780,"height":110,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"1000000000000003","type":"text","text":"**unitree_go2_spatial**\n\nロボット基盤 + 知覚 + 地図","x":40,"y":180,"width":340,"height":150,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"1000000000000004","type":"text","text":"**McpServer**\n\nスキルを MCP ツールとして公開","x":400,"y":180,"width":340,"height":150,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"1000000000000005","type":"text","text":"**★ AzureVoiceLiveAgent**\n\nSTT + LLM + TTS を 1 本の WS で処理\n(McpClient を置き換え)","x":760,"y":180,"width":340,"height":150,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"1000000000000006","type":"text","text":"**★ PttKeyboard**\n\npynput global hotkey (既定 `F9`, `$DIMOS_PTT_KEY` で変更)\n押下中だけ `mic_gate=True` を publish → AzureVoiceLiveAgent","x":1120,"y":180,"width":340,"height":150,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"1000000000000007","type":"text","text":"**SecurityModule** ※ `.disabled_modules` で無効化\n\n会話 TTS は Voice Live 側で完結し、SpeakSkill 経路を持たない\n(MCP 二重発話のリスクを避けるため SecurityModule ごと無効)","x":1480,"y":180,"width":340,"height":150,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"2000000000000002","type":"text","text":"NavigationSkillContainer","x":40,"y":450,"width":840,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2000000000000003","type":"text","text":"PersonFollowSkillContainer  (camera_info = GO2Connection)","x":40,"y":530,"width":840,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2000000000000004","type":"text","text":"UnitreeSkillContainer","x":40,"y":610,"width":840,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"2000000000000005","type":"text","text":"**★ PttKeyboard**\n`F9` 押下中 = `mic_gate=True` (pynput global hotkey, `$DIMOS_PTT_KEY` で変更可)","x":40,"y":700,"width":840,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"2000000000000006","type":"text","text":"**SpeakSkill / WebInputAudioOnly は配線しない**\nSecurityModule は `.disabled_modules` で無効化。会話 TTS は Voice Live 側の `_VoicePlayback` で完結。\nWebUI マイクはスピーカー出力のエコーで誤発火するため未配線 (PTT ローカルマイクのみ)。","x":40,"y":800,"width":840,"height":120,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"3000000000000002","type":"text","text":"**unitree_go2**  (basic + mapping + nav planners + MovementManager)","x":980,"y":450,"width":840,"height":80,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"3000000000000003","type":"text","text":"SpatialMemory","x":980,"y":540,"width":840,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"3000000000000004","type":"text","text":"PerceiveLoopSkill","x":980,"y":620,"width":840,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"3000000000000005","type":"text","text":"SecurityModule  ※ `.disabled_modules(SecurityModule)` で無効化 (SpeakSkill 二重発話を避けるため)","x":980,"y":700,"width":840,"height":70,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"3000000000000006","type":"text","text":"GO2Connection  (WebRTC)","x":980,"y":780,"width":840,"height":70,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4000000000000010","type":"text","text":"[ユーザー音声]","x":40,"y":1060,"width":160,"height":70,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000011","type":"text","text":"**SounddeviceAudioSource**\n(mic, 24 kHz PCM16, `mic_gate` で gate)","x":220,"y":1060,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000012","type":"text","text":"base64 PCM\n`input_audio_buffer.append`\n(gate 閉時は zero-fill で server VAD 継続)","x":500,"y":1060,"width":260,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000013","type":"text","text":"**Azure Voice Live WS**\n`voicelive_connect` (gpt-realtime)\nServerVad + EchoCancel + NoiseSup","x":780,"y":1040,"width":320,"height":120,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000014","type":"text","text":"**pending function_call**\n`response.function_call_arguments.done`\n→ `_active.pending_calls.append(...)`","x":1120,"y":1040,"width":340,"height":100,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000015","type":"text","text":"**McpAdapter** (HTTP `localhost:9990/mcp`)\n→ McpServer → スキル実行","x":1480,"y":1040,"width":340,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000016","type":"text","text":"`function_call_output` を Voice Live に返す\n`report_after_tools` のみ `_issue_response(trigger='tool_result')` で報告","x":1120,"y":1145,"width":700,"height":70,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000017","type":"text","text":"MovementManager → GO2Connection → 犬","x":1480,"y":1220,"width":340,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4000000000000020","type":"text","text":"**PttKeyboard**\n`F9` 押下中だけ `mic_gate=True`\n(`$DIMOS_PTT_KEY` で変更可)","x":40,"y":1220,"width":380,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000021","type":"text","text":"**tool_stream** (progress / log notifications)\nツール進捗を `[tool:name] ...` として注入","x":440,"y":1220,"width":420,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000030","type":"text","text":"`response.audio.delta`\n(PCM16 24 kHz)","x":780,"y":1320,"width":320,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000031","type":"text","text":"**_VoicePlayback**\nsd.OutputStream callback + cancel-queue","x":440,"y":1320,"width":320,"height":80,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000032","type":"text","text":"[スピーカー]","x":260,"y":1320,"width":160,"height":80,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"4000000000000040","type":"text","text":"**バージイン**: `input_audio_buffer.speech_started` →\n`_VoicePlayback.skip_pending()` + `response.cancel`","x":1120,"y":1320,"width":700,"height":80,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"4000000000000050","type":"text","text":"`agent` Out: `AIMessage`(最終テキスト)  ·  `agent_idle` Out: bool  ·  `RESPONSE_CREATED`→False / `RESPONSE_DONE`→True","x":880,"y":1460,"width":940,"height":60,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"4000000000000061","type":"text","text":"`RESPONSE_DONE`\n→ `active.snapshot()` を取り `_active=None`\n→ `active.done.set()` で waiter 解放\n→ `trigger=='user'` のみ `_on_response_done()` を task 起動","x":1280,"y":1540,"width":300,"height":150,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000062","type":"text","text":"**`_issue_response(ResponseRequest)`**\n1) `_ActiveResponse(trigger=…)` を pre-build\n2) `_pending_active` に置く\n3) `response.create(...)` 送信\n4) `RESPONSE_CREATED` が `_pending_active` を\n   `_active` へ昇格\n5) `active.done.wait()` で待機 → snapshot 返却","x":1600,"y":1540,"width":240,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000063","type":"text","text":"`_on_response_done()` で pending tools を直列実行\n`発話 → tool 実行 → (必要なら) tool_result 報告`\n非 report tool は完全 silent (response.create を出さない)","x":1280,"y":1710,"width":300,"height":140,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"4000000000000064","type":"text","text":"**バージイン時の解除**\n`SPEECH_STARTED` で `_active.pending_calls=[]`\n+ `_active.done.set()` + `_active=None` + `_pending_active=None`\n→ `_issue_response` 内の `done.wait()` も即解放","x":880,"y":1770,"width":380,"height":110,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"5000000000000001","type":"text","text":"**凡例**  ·  紫=合成ルート  ·  シアン=upstream モジュール  ·  オレンジ=★ Voice Live 差分  ·  緑=データフロー / ロボット制御  ·  赤=バージイン制御\n\n**voice-live が agentic-ja と異なる主な点**: \n1) `McpClient + WhisperNode + JapaneseSpeakSkill` を 1 本の `AzureVoiceLiveAgent` に統合 (gpt-realtime / ja-JP-NanamiNeural)  \n2) マイクは `SounddeviceAudioSource` から base64 PCM を直接 Voice Live WS に流す (Whisper を経由しない)  \n3) 出力 TTS は WS から届く 24 kHz PCM を `_VoicePlayback` (sd.OutputStream) で即時再生  \n4) MCP は `function_call` ↔ `function_call_output` で双方向ブリッジ (`McpAdapter` 経由)  \n5) **forced-speech / tool 報告は `_issue_response(ResponseRequest)` で発火**: `_ActiveResponse` を pre-build → `_pending_active` → `RESPONSE_CREATED` が昇格 → インスタンス所有 `done` で待機。`_next_trigger` / 共有 `_resp_done_event` の競合を排除  \n6) **response 単位状態は `_ActiveResponse` に集約**: `_resp_had_audio` / `_resp_pending_calls` / `_resp_text_buf` / `_resp_trigger` を 1 つの dataclass に統合 (`_ResponseSnapshot` は `active.snapshot()` 経由でのみ生成)  \n7) バージイン: 再生キュー破棄 + `response.cancel` + `_active.done.set()` で pending waiter 解放  \n8) `SecurityModule` は `.disabled_modules` で無効化 — `SpeakSkill` は配線せず、会話 TTS は Voice Live 側 (`_VoicePlayback`) で完結  \n9) マイクは `PttKeyboard` (既定 `F9`, `$DIMOS_PTT_KEY` で変更) が `mic_gate` を駆動し、AzureVoiceLiveAgent 内蔵 `SounddeviceAudioSource` をゲート (WebUI マイクはエコー誤発火回避のため未配線)","x":0,"y":1910,"width":1860,"height":320,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"4000000000000060","type":"text","text":"**`_ActiveResponse` (per-response 状態)**\n`trigger` = `user` / `preface_forced` / `tool_result`\n`had_audio` / `pending_calls` / `text_buf`\n`done: asyncio.Event` (各インスタンス所有)\n\n`RESPONSE_CREATED` で構築、`RESPONSE_DONE` または\n`SPEECH_STARTED` で破棄。","x":880,"y":1540,"width":380,"height":210,"color":"2"}
	],
